title: Silverstar House
story: After being destroyed in a great battle several centuries ago the house remained deserted. Currently it is overrun with wasps.

notes.text: A mundane-looking door, pleads to be killed when the knob is touched.
A huge stone double door with a keyhole to the north.
A rear entrance into the house.
A cold barbarian, lying in a corner.
A skinless body of a halfling, an eye-shaped key close by.
A reinforced basket with a hammer of life stealing.
